# Note: src/routeTree.gen.ts is intentionally NOT ignored. The Vite
# TanStack Router plugin regenerates it during `vite build`, but the
# preceding `tsc -b` step needs it on disk to type-check. The committed
# copy is always in sync with the routes — easier than splitting the
# build into two stages.
